OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FShe was dying, and for a short period
OL,7,Fof time she was dying in pain.
OL,9,FThat is when we were referred to our
OL,10,Flocal hospice. Hospices cannot save
OL,11,Fyou, but they save you from the worst
OL,12,Fof what dying can bring.
OL,14,FThey saved my mum from dying in pain,
OL,15,Fand they saved her from dying in a
OL,16,Fhospital.
