OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FAn ageing population living longer
OL,7,Fwith terminal health conditions means
OL,8,Fhospices are treating more people than
OL,9,Fever, at a time when the cost of
OL,10,Fliving is limiting the amount of money
OL,11,Fcoming through the door in donations.
OL,13,FData given exclusively to the Tonight
OL,14,Fprogramme by Hospice UK reveals 70% of
OL,15,Fhospices are in financial deficit this
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/27
