OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"We estimate that the hospice sector
OL,7,Fas a whole could be facing spending a
OL,8,Fhundred million pounds more than it
OL,9,Fgets in income," Toby Porter, Chief
OL,10,FExecutive of Hopsice UK, told us.
OL,12,F"That is not a sustainable. The sector
OL,13,Fwill just simply start to shrivel."
OL,15,FThe financial pressures keep coming.
OL,16,FWhen the government announces pay
OL,17,Frises for NHS staff, as it did
OL,18,Frecently, most hospices agree to meet
OL,19,Fthe increase in order to retain nurses
OL,20,Fand doctors, but they don't get any
OL,21,Fgovernment funding to pay for it.
