OL,6,FThe money has to come from through
OL,7,Fmore fundraising.
OL,9,FOn top of that, the recent national
OL,10,Finsurance increase in the budget will
OL,11,Falso hit hospices, who are not exempt.
OL,13,FWe understand discussions are taking
OL,14,Fplace between the sector and
OL,15,Fgovernment ministers.
OL,17,FI have been told the sector has asked
OL,18,Fthe Department of Health for an
OL,19,Fimmediate cash injection of #110m to
OL,20,Favoid cuts to services and jobs before
OL,21,FChristmas.
