OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FFor our special Tonight programme, I
OL,7,Fwent been back to St Giles Hospice in
OL,8,FStaffordshire. It is more than a
OL,9,Fdecade since they helped my mum, but
OL,10,Fthings have changed.
OL,12,FJust 18% of St Giles' funding comes
OL,13,Ffrom the government.
OL,15,FIt means they need to raise more than
OL,16,F#8 million from the local community
OL,17,Fevery year just to stay open, but not
OL,18,Fenough money is coming in.
