OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FThe hospice has had to cut 22 jobs
OL,7,Fthis month, and reduce the services it
OL,8,Fprovides. Standing in an empty
OL,9,Finpatient room, St Giles CEO Elinor
OL,10,FEustice tells me it is "madness".
OL,12,F"We've got 23 beds here on our
OL,13,Finpatient unit," she said. "We can
OL,14,Fonly afford to run 15, so a room like
OL,15,Fthis is going to be empty because we
OL,16,Fare not able to staff this inpatient
OL,17,Funit.
