OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FIn 2019, her dad Tony was diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith kidney cancer. He was a TV
OL,8,Fpresenter at the time, a legend of
OL,9,Fregional news at ITV Granada Reports
OL,10,Fin the northwest of England.
OL,12,FAs his condition deteriorated, he
OL,13,Freceived end-of-life care at Bury
OL,14,FHospice in Lancashire, and Natalie was
OL,15,Fblown away by the treatment.
OL,17,F"I was shocked. I couldn't believe
OL,18,Fthat these places existed," she told
OL,19,Fme.
