OL,6,F"My dad had this huge room all to
OL,7,Fhimself, windows that looked out onto
OL,8,Fthis beautiful garden. It felt like we
OL,9,Fwere in our own little bubble. We
OL,10,Fcould be together.
OL,12,F"I just think (the staff) are like
OL,13,Fangels on earth, which sounds so over
OL,14,Fthe top, but that's genuinely how it
OL,15,Ffelt in that moment because I'd never
OL,16,Fexperienced such compassion, such
OL,17,Fcare."
