OL,6,F"We didn't get that privacy that we
OL,7,Fwere hoping for, we didn't get that
OL,8,Fspace.
OL,10,F"It was heartbreaking to see her in a
OL,11,Fposition where she'd been so
OL,12,Fmeticulous, so careful, so proactive,
OL,13,Fso brave, to then not have the
OL,14,Fexperience that she'd so carefully
OL,15,Fplanned for and hoped for.
OL,17,F"This is a crucial time. You don't get
OL,18,Fa second chance at this. When someone
OL,19,Fis in the last days of their life, you
OL,20,Fdon't get a do over."
