OL,7,Ftold ITV News' Daniel Hewitt she has
OL,8,Fput her house on the market to move
OL,9,Fsomewhere close to a hospice
OL,11,FOn top of the huge financial
OL,12,Fpressures, hospices could be about to
OL,13,Fgrapple with an enormous challenge.
OL,15,FA new bill on assisted dying is set to
OL,16,Fbe debated in Parliament on Friday, a
OL,17,Fcontroversial new law which would
OL,18,Fallow people with a terminal illness
OL,19,Fto end their own life.
