OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,FSome in the sector believe palliative
OL,7,Fcare needs to be improved first,
OL,8,Fbefore such a momentous decision is
OL,9,Fmade.
OL,11,F"We carried out a survey in September
OL,12,Fof this year," said Professor
OL,13,FKatherine Sleeman, an expert in
OL,14,Fpalliative medicine at Kings College
OL,15,FLondon.
OL,17,F"We found that 83% of people who
OL,18,Fsupport assisted dying legalisation
OL,19,Fcite poor palliative care as a reason
OL,20,Ffor their support.
