OL,3,C'It is heartbreaking': Hospices under
OL,4,Cpressure as 70% face financial deficit
OL,6,F"It does really concern me that
OL,7,Flegalising assisted dying in the
OL,8,Fcontext of patchy and often inadequate
OL,9,Fpalliative and end of life care
OL,10,Fservices will lead people to choosing
OL,11,Fit simply because they can't get the
OL,12,Fcare they need.
OL,14,F"That, to me, is very concerning and
OL,15,Fneeds to be thought about very, very
OL,16,Fdeeply."
