OL,6,FThe government declined an interview
OL,7,Ffor the Tonight programme. In a
OL,8,Fstatement they told us they are
OL,9,Fdetermined to make sure everyone has
OL,10,Faccess to high quality end-of-life
OL,11,Fcare and thank the public for their
OL,12,Fgenerous donations.
OL,14,FHospices, they said, have a big role
OL,15,Fto play in the shift towards moving
OL,16,Fmore healthcare into the community.
OL,18,FYou can watch the full Tonight
OL,19,Fprogramme, 'Keeping Care Alive:
OL,20,FHospices in Crisis?', on ITV and ITVX
OL,21,Fat 8.30pm on Thursday, November 28.
